					<div>
						<pb n="150"/><p><lb/>Im <placeName ref="loc007683.02">bösen turn</placeName>
							<seg><lb/><origDate when="1620-09-16"><num value="16">xvi</num> <foreign xml:lang="la"><choice><abbr>7bris</abbr><expan>septembris</expan></choice></foreign> <hi rend="underline">1620</hi></origDate>, <choice><abbr>j</abbr><expan>judex</expan></choice> <abbr>h</abbr> <choice><abbr>groß</abbr><expan>großweibel</expan></choice><note>Gemeint ist <persName ref="per009249">Daniel von Montenach</persName>.</note></seg>
							<seg><lb/><abbr>H</abbr> <persName ref="per009250">Gerwer</persName>, <abbr>h</abbr> <persName ref="per009255">Affry</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><persName ref="per009251">Känel</persName>, <persName ref="per009123a.03">Werli</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><persName ref="per009392">Werli</persName></seg>
						<seg><lb/>Weybel</seg></p>
						<p><gap reason="irrelevant"/><note>Die ersten Abschnitte betreffen andere Personen, darunter den Prozess gegen <persName>Catry Hans</persName>. Vgl. <ref target="urn:ssrq:SSRQ-FR-I_2_8-52.6-1">SSRQ FR I/2/8 52.6-1</ref>.</note></p>
						<p><lb/><foreign xml:lang="la">Bis</foreign><note>Vermutlich wurde der Angeklagte zum zweiten Mal verhört.</note></p>
							<p><foreign xml:lang="la">Ibidem</foreign><note>Das Verhör fand im <placeName ref="loc007683">Bösen Turm</placeName> statt.</note></p>
						<p><seg><lb/><add place="left margin">Hat nüt bezalt.</add></seg>
							<seg><persName ref="per009569">Pierre Bosson</persName><note>Pierre Bosson sera condamné et exécuté en 1623. Voir <ref target="urn:ssrq:SSRQ-FR-I_2_8-56.41-1">SSRQ FR I/2/8 56.41-1</ref>.</note>, de <placeName ref="loc007647.03">Romond</placeName>, ne sait qu’il aye <term ref="lem015635.24">ballé</term>
								<lb/>aulcune <term ref="lem018382.02">graise</term> a <persName ref="per009614a.01">Hausy Malley</persName>, disant
						<lb/>luy faire grand tort de l’<term ref="lem015356.06">acculper</term> de
						<lb/>cela&#160;; que veritablement il auroit prins
								<lb/>du pain, <term ref="lem018643.01">fromage</term> et fruit, mais non pas
						<lb/>aultre chose.</seg></p>
						<pb n="151"/><p><lb/><foreign xml:lang="la">Ibidem</foreign><note>Das Verhör fand im <placeName ref="loc007683">Bösen Turm</placeName> statt.</note></p>
						<p><seg><lb/><add place="left margin">Hat nüt bezalt.</add></seg>
							<seg><persName ref="per009614a.01">Hausy Malley</persName> faisant du commencement ne<lb break="no"/>gative de sa primiere <term ref="lem019465.01">confession</term>, neantmoins
								<lb/>en la fin l’a confirmé, <term ref="lem015549.03">confessant</term> son
								<lb/><term ref="lem019555.05">maistre</term> le seroit venu trouver <add place="above">de nuict</add> aux prisons,
								<lb/>luy commandant de se retirer de sa <term ref="lem019465.01">confes<lb break="no"/>sion</term> et la nyer, et qu’on luy porteroit
								<lb/>le lendemain le <choice><abbr>s<hi rend="sup">t</hi></abbr><expan>saint</expan></choice> <term ref="lem019546.01">sacrement</term>, lequel
						<lb/>devoit remettre hors de la bouche.</seg>
						<seg><lb/>Disant dadvantage que tout ce qu’il a cy<lb break="no"/>devant <term ref="lem015549.07">confessé</term> estre que trop veritable,
						<lb/>hormis de ne s’avoir oublié avec les <term ref="lem015407.03">pudres</term>,
							<lb/>que seulement avec la <subst><del>bl</del><add place="inline"><term ref="lem019396.01">brebis</term></add></subst> et la
						<lb/><term ref="lem015014">moge</term>.</seg> <seg>En aprés ledit <persName ref="per009569">Bosson</persName> estant
						<lb/>confronté avec ledit <persName ref="per009614a.07">Maley</persName>, il a dit n’estre
						<lb/><persName ref="per009618">Pierre Brasey</persName>, lequel luy a <term ref="lem015635.24">ballé</term> de la
							<lb/><term ref="lem018382.02">graise</term>&#160;; que n’a jamais accusé ledit <persName ref="per009569">Bosson</persName>,
						<lb/>duquel ne sait aulcun mal. Aultre n’a
						<lb/>dit.</seg>
							<seg><add place="left margin">Hingericht <origDate when="1620-09-18">18
						<lb/><foreign xml:lang="la"><choice><abbr>7br</abbr><expan>septembris</expan></choice></foreign> <hi rend="underline">1620</hi></origDate></add><note>Der Schreiber hat sich wohl geirrt: Laut den Ratsprotokollen fand die Hinrichtung am <date when="1620-09-19">19. September 1620</date> statt.</note></seg></p>
